761
00:54:45,900 --> 00:54:49,766
Tonight, my secretary has to shine just as brightly as I do.

762
00:54:49,766 --> 00:54:54,011
Let me recheck the stage, then I'll change my outfit.

763
00:54:54,011 --> 00:54:57,966
I never knew your event organizing skills were this professional.

764
00:54:57,966 --> 00:55:00,866
You could start your own company with these skills!

765
00:55:02,100 --> 00:55:05,766
I haven't thought about what I want to do next yet.

766
00:55:09,033 --> 00:55:12,700
I want to find something I truly enjoy,

767
00:55:12,700 --> 00:55:15,166
and go on a date with someone.

768
00:55:21,397 --> 00:55:22,997
A date!

769
00:55:23,500 --> 00:55:26,900
Yes, one day I will have a family.

770
00:55:26,900 --> 00:55:31,633
If I meet the right person, I might even get married.

771
00:55:33,566 --> 00:55:37,054
But the other day, when I saw you, I thought you were in love with…

772
00:55:37,054 --> 00:55:39,170
What do you mean?

773
00:55:39,170 --> 00:55:43,190
Never mind. Forget about it.

774
00:55:45,166 --> 00:55:47,666
All right, I understand you now.

775
00:55:47,666 --> 00:55:51,833
Your life should be yours. I won't hold you back anymore.

776
00:55:55,000 --> 00:55:57,800
Feel free to announce the search for a new secretary.

777
00:56:13,100 --> 00:56:14,533
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

778
00:56:14,533 --> 00:56:16,333
How long have you stayed in Thailand?

779
00:56:16,333 --> 00:56:18,166
A couple of years.

780
00:56:18,700 --> 00:56:20,900
Everyone, a big smile, please.

781
00:56:30,966 --> 00:56:32,200
- Hello.
- Thank you for coming.

782
00:56:32,200 --> 00:56:34,166
My pleasure, nice to meet you.

783
00:56:34,166 --> 00:56:36,131
Okay, I'm going to have to greet my friends.

784
00:56:36,131 --> 00:56:38,466
- Okay, take your time.
- Thanks.

785
00:57:11,233 --> 00:57:13,433
Is something wrong, Boss?

786
00:57:15,691 --> 00:57:17,291
No.

787
00:57:18,303 --> 00:57:21,100
Are all the VIP guests here yet?

788
00:57:21,100 --> 00:57:24,866
Yes, they're all here. Mr. Li Tang is especially eager to meet you.

789
00:57:29,166 --> 00:57:32,200
Next year, I'll go explore opportunities in Beijing.

790
00:57:32,200 --> 00:57:34,600
I'd like to open a new branch there.

791
00:57:34,600 --> 00:57:38,433
That's wonderful. China will always be happy to welcome you.

792
00:57:38,433 --> 00:57:42,033
Tomorrow, we've arranged a dinner cruise

793
00:57:42,033 --> 00:57:46,448
on the Chao Phraya River for you and your wife.

794
00:57:47,275 --> 00:57:49,133
Thank you so much, Ms. Prim.

795
00:57:49,133 --> 00:57:50,866
You really know my wife well.

796
00:57:50,866 --> 00:57:53,887
She's been wanting to go on a river cruise for a long time.

797
00:57:54,566 --> 00:57:56,533
I love the suite room very much.

798
00:57:56,533 --> 00:58:00,033
Thanks to your wife for managing this for me.

799
00:58:00,033 --> 00:58:03,366
Actually, she is my secretary, not my wife.

800
00:58:04,123 --> 00:58:07,100
I made a fool of myself.

801
00:58:07,100 --> 00:58:10,266
I've done more embarrassing things than you.

802
00:58:10,266 --> 00:58:11,810
Sorry.

803
00:58:12,433 --> 00:58:16,733
All right, everyone, it's almost time to count down to the New Year!

804
00:58:16,733 --> 00:58:20,766
Is everyone ready to count down?

805
00:58:26,233 --> 00:58:29,066
Boss, you should go to the fireworks viewing spot.

806
00:58:29,066 --> 00:58:30,910
Come with me.

807
00:58:32,000 --> 00:58:35,100
You never stay for the countdown with me.

808
00:58:35,100 --> 00:58:37,133
But this year,

809
00:58:37,566 --> 00:58:39,533
you have to stay.

810
00:58:44,866 --> 00:58:47,164
Okay, guys, cheers!

811
00:58:48,033 --> 00:58:49,666
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

812
00:58:49,666 --> 00:58:53,200
All right then, let's count down together!

813
00:58:53,200 --> 00:58:56,833
Boss, can I check on things first?

814
00:58:56,833 --> 00:59:00,333
There are plenty of staff for that. You don't need to worry anymore.

815
00:59:00,333 --> 00:59:02,300
Stay here with me.

816
00:59:03,748 --> 00:59:05,248
10…

817
00:59:07,062 --> 00:59:08,672
9…

818
00:59:10,508 --> 00:59:12,048
8…

819
00:59:13,914 --> 00:59:15,600
7…

820
00:59:15,600 --> 00:59:17,400
I'm really sorry, Boss.

821
00:59:17,400 --> 00:59:19,064
6…

822
00:59:20,400 --> 00:59:22,140
5…

823
00:59:22,883 --> 00:59:24,585
4…

824
00:59:25,667 --> 00:59:27,367
3…

825
00:59:28,190 --> 00:59:29,764
2…

826
00:59:32,358 --> 00:59:33,858
1…

827
00:59:38,066 --> 00:59:40,400
Happy New Year!

828
01:00:21,900 --> 01:00:26,966
<i>♪ Sleep now, my dear, my precious one ♪</i>

829
01:00:26,966 --> 01:00:32,633
<i>♪ Sleep tight, may your dreams be sweet ♪</i>

830
01:00:32,633 --> 01:00:37,733
<i>♪ with stars filling the sky above just for you ♪</i>

831
01:00:37,733 --> 01:00:42,500
<i>♪ I'll always be right here ♪</i>

832
01:00:43,200 --> 01:00:47,566
<i>♪ La la la la laa la la ♪</i>

833
01:00:48,160 --> 01:00:52,300
<i>♪ La la la la laa laa la… ♪</i>

834
01:00:53,866 --> 01:00:58,833
<i>♪ I'm still right here, close to you ♪</i>

835
01:00:58,833 --> 01:01:03,866
<i>♪ Always ready to hold you in my arms ♪</i>

836
01:01:19,960 --> 01:01:21,593
<i>Peekaboo!
[Next Episode]</i>

837
01:01:21,593 --> 01:01:23,851
<i>Just take care of Ploen for one day.</i>

838
01:01:23,851 --> 01:01:25,780
<i>But I have to find a new secretary for the boss.</i>

839
01:01:25,780 --> 01:01:28,170
<i>How can I look after her?</i>

840
01:01:29,618 --> 01:01:32,336
<i>What is it like to be a good secretary?</i>

841
01:01:32,336 --> 01:01:34,378
<i>You have to take care of your valuables as best you can.</i>

842
01:01:34,378 --> 01:01:38,057
<i>And for the secretary, the most valuable thing is him.</i>

843
01:01:38,706 --> 01:01:40,032
<i>I will let you redeem yourself</i>

844
01:01:40,032 --> 01:01:42,854
<i>by training your assistant secretary to pass the probation.</i>

845
01:01:42,854 --> 01:01:46,281
<i>Then I will allow you to resign.</i>
